{
    "info": {
        "name": "Verso-Backend API",
        "description": "REST API collection for Verso-Backend sovereign business operating system.\n\n## Authentication\nAll requests require Bearer token authentication.\n\n## Setup\n1. Create an API key in Admin â†’ API Keys\n2. Add the key to the `api_key` environment variable\n3. Set `base_url` to your server URL",
